I"<h2 id="introduction">Introduction</h2>

<p>C# is an Object Oriented Programming language and it has many similarities to Java, C++ and VB. In fact, C#
combines the power and efficiency of C++, the simple and clean object oriented design of Java and the language simplification of Visual Basic.</p>

<h3 id="writing-your-first-hello-world-program-in-c">Writing Your First Hello World Program in C#</h3>

<p>We can use any Text Editor for writting a C# program. We will use Visual Studio Code for this course.</p>

<p>Open Visual Studio Code. Create a new file and name it as Program.cs. Write below Code and save the file.</p>

